translated: Munckhammar, Anders Olov, lawyer, Varberg, born on June 26, 1903 in Bromma, Stockholm county, son of G.E. Munckhammar and Ida Carlsson. Married on 1930 to Karin Gustavsson. Children: Anita born in 1932, Bertil born in 1934. Completed high school in 1922, graduated with a law degree in Uppsala in 1928. Worked as a court assistant in Halmstad district court from 1929 to 1932, then started his own law firm in Varberg from 1933. Secretary in the board of Varberg, Träslöv municipality and others.
